guideos-keyring (1.0-1) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Add GuideOS repository configuration and GPG keys
  * Support for GuideOS Cinnamon, Trixie and Universe repositories
  * Use modern deb822 sources format
  * Include APT configuration to suppress modernize-sources warnings
  * Automatically remove old .list format repository files
  * Automatically migrate GPG keys from old to new location
  * Provide detailed installation feedback and status messages

